Java based client For ChargeBee and MongoDB

Dependencies:
    ChargeBee latest Java library
    MongoDB NoSQL database
    Latest MongoDB Java Driver

Key Points:
    In the starting window you can provide the appropriate ChargeBee Site and 
    the API key provided also from ChargeBee.

    Java client need a valid installation of MongoDB listening for incoming
    connections in the default port. Also it creates a database for testing
    called testdb.

    You can connect to a test site hosted by ChargeBee and retrieve the stored
    data.
